title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Nov 10 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Nov 10 2021
description:
Clay & Buck join the Rittenhouse trial live and offer commentary on what's looking like a clear case of self-defense during the Kenosha BLM riots. Putting the 17-year-old defendant on the stand is a bold move, and his breaking down in tears could only help his case. Biden sends inflation skyrocketing at highest rate in 31 years.
